1. Requires CONFIG_SAMPLE_TRACE_EVENTS enabled
2. Custom trace definitions go to custom-traces.h as TRACING(name)
3. Using trace: TRACING_TAP(name);
4. API: /sys/kernel/debug/tracing.
   events/sample/enable - enable/disable all tracepoints
   events/sample/tracing_name/enable - enable/disable tracepoint name
   trace - log of all tracepoints including name, current task name and rdtsc timestamp
